<section class="py-24 px-4">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
    <h1 class="text-5xl sm:text-6xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-6">
      Your media,<br />
      <span class="text-primary">your server</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-base-content/70 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 leading-relaxed">
      Mydia is a self-hosted media management app for organizing and tracking your TV shows and movies.
      Automatic metadata, P2P remote access, and complete control over your collection.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3">
      <a
        href="https://github.com/getmydia/mydia"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="btn btn-primary btn-lg"
      >
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
